<br>
The damage on them seem so low that I am hoping this is the case (otherwise, why the heck would someone use Moonblades that do 7-14 over your fists that do way more).  The concept would be similar to using brass knuckles to enhance your &quot;melee&quot; damage over bare fists.  Can you guys please confirm this before I dump tons of IP into 1he, etc?  <br>
<br>
If this is not the case, IP is much better spent on program requs vs weapon abilities, cause moonblades would be totally worthless.<br>
<br>
Thanks<br>
<br>
